doctype html
include includes/head.jade
  block title
    | - theright.fit
    
body
  .container
    include includes/logo-works.jade
        
    .row
      h1.darkgrey.introwork theright.fit

  .container.wide.fullonmobile
    .row
      .twelve.columns
        img(src="imgs/trf/theright.fit-logo.png" srcset="imgs/trf/theright.fit-logo@2x.png 2x")
          
  .container.margins
    .row
      .twelve.columns.company-desc 
        p
          a(href="https://theright.fit/", target="_blank") Theright.fit
          |  is a start up launched by Taryn Williams and Aurelien Labonne that aims to revolutionise the modelling and talent industry by removing hidden commissions and bias, empowering users of the platform with the information and facts they need to make informed decisions about their next job or casting. 
  .container
    .row
      hr
      h6 brief  
      h3.darkgrey A new brand
    .row
      .nine.columns
        p Theright.fit needed a fashionable brand that could represent the concept of the choosing the perfect talent for the job. I designed the branding and the identity - creating a recognizable visual language for online and offline applications.
      .three.columns.lightgrey
        .caption.left
            li Branding
            li Corporate Identity
            li Icons Design
            
  .container.wide.fullonmobile
    .row
      .twelve.columns
        img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-logomark.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-logomark@2x.png 2x")
  .container  
    .row
      .offset-by-two.eight.columns.caption
          .title Above 
          | A simplified variation of the logomark designed to support small applications.
          
  .full.black
    .container
      .row
        .twelve.columns.margin-top
          img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-grid.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-grid@2x.png 2x")

    .container
      .row.margin-top
        .offset-by-two.eight.columns.caption
            .title Above 
            | The pattern works in parallel with the logomark to define the identity and the yellow dot rappresents the selected "Right Talent". The patter can be applied in different ways based on the usage. 

  .container.margins
    .row
      .container
        .row.margin-top
        .twelve.columns
          img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-display.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-display@2x.png 2x")
    
  .full.trf

    .container
      .row
        .twelve.columns
          img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-diplay-2.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-diplay-2@2x.png 2x")
    .container
      .offset-by-two.eight.columns.caption
          .title Above 
          | An example of the identity applied, using multiple images in conjunction with the logomark and the pattern.

  .full.black
    .container
      .row
        .offset-by-one.ten.columns
          img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-big-icons.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-big-icons@2x.png 2x")

    .container.wide
      .row
        .offset-by-one.ten.columns
          img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-all-icons.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-all-icons@2x.png 2x")
      .row
        .offset-by-two.nine.columns.caption
            .title Above
            | The icons design is based on the primary typeface Brandon - maintening the same boldness and roundness as the typeface.

  .container
    .row
      .twelve.columns.margins
        img(src="imgs/trf/therightfit-website.png" srcset="imgs/trf/therightfit-website@2x.png 2x")

include includes/footer-js.jade
